chtverhältnisse in unterschiedlichen Kontexten und zeigen die Kontingenz und Relationalität gesellschaftlicher Praktiken auf.Der Band trägt zur kritischen Analyse des Verhältnisses von Theorie, Kultur und Gesellschaft im 21. Jahrhundert bei.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aCultural Studies. 4aGesellschaft. 4aKontingenz. 4aKultur. 4aKultursoziologie. 4aKulturtheorie. 4aKulturwissenschaft. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Popular Culture.2bisacsh  aCultural Studies.  aCultural Theory.  aSociety.  aSociology of Culture.1 aBishop, Ryan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCouldry, Nick, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFeatherstone, Mike, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHardt, Hanno, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJin, Huimin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKellner, Douglas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLash, Scott, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRyan, Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWinter, Rainer, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWinter, Rainer, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2010-2013z9783110352856oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Lit. & Kultur 2010-2013z978311037074440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/transcript.9783839409855zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839409855423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839409855/original  a978-3-11-